Introduction

Universe Cowards (Korean: 우주겁쟁이; Japanese: 宇宙の臆病者) (also known as Universe Hipsters (우주힙쟁이)) is a duo consisting of Super Junior's Kim Heechul and BUZZ' Min Kyunghoon.
They originally debuted as a project duo on the show Knowing Brothers and released their first single "Sweet Dream (나비잠)" under SM Station Season 1.
The group name is a mix between Heechul's nickname "Universe Big Star" and BUZZ's hit song "Coward".
